{"tid":459066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港共人治] 羅范椒芬：國歌法難詳列場景　市民要「執生」","createTime":"2017-11-05T12:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T01:50:14.000Z","uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"084a3eac7bd0bee81d6df43e43becf39f6800d05","tid":459066,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國人大代表羅范椒芬認為，國歌法的法例難以詳列所有場景，如何尊重國歌市民要「執生」；立法會議員梁美芬則說，國歌法在民事訴訟方面或有追溯力。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會周六通過 把國歌法納入基本法附件三。港區人大代表羅范椒芬表示，各界不需要令國歌法問題複雜化，或想得太極端。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬表示，即使國歌法的刑事條例未必定下追溯期，但在民事法中或有追溯力。梁美芬又表示，在本地立法的過程需要清楚定義「在場」、「肅立」及「莊重」三個核心概念，相信能夠從法律條文中解決。<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母臭閪隻死老妖幾撚時仆街冚家剷死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cae09910f3c8d5259651b1c5f39968f069c2916","tid":459066,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=242064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D242064&d=Hvgrx4ZACs2XLgKAvaCYyoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=075bd15f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D242064&h=bdd79f21\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=242064</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/SONG.FANNY.BITE.1900.0111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FSONG.FANNY.BITE.1900.0111.jpg&h=08adfbd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64e6e4c411991185b3c15d1d871dc58967cdb369","tid":459066,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"你條臭西都痴撚線 法律要人執生"},{"pid":"6da4ecdd2160bae3fe9874e10d1642fd19b0e9bb","tid":459066,"ui